(0) login to scalar.scitec.kobe-u.ac.jp.
(1) check grid size (NX,NY,NZ) in constants.f90
(2) Edit target.f90
(3) Check FFLAGS in Makefile
(4) make nloop_list.txt
(5) Edit nloop_list.txt to reduce the target figure nloops.
(6) make plot_data_generator
(7) make figs
(8) check the directory 'Workfiles'. Eps files should be there.
(9) make gif

  
